eZ trade changelog:
-------------------

Changes from version 1.0.5
--------------------------
* Optimized communication with the database, it's now faster and uses less memory
* Added Indonesian translation
* Added showing of hours, minutes and seconds idle on session info

Changes from version 1.0.4
--------------------------
* Added image previews in hot deals list.
* Speedup by 20-50%, due to more efficient ini file reading.
* Added increasment of product count in basket/wishlist when adding a product with the same options.
* Fixed deleting of products from the wishlist.
* Fixed broken product search.
* Fixed the article search.
* Fixed the product search, does not output {next} and {prev}

Changes from version 1.0.3
--------------------------
* Added French, German, Spanish and Czech translation
* Added possibility to set session timeout to infinity (0)
* Added clickable images in articlepreview in admin
* Fixed a session timeout bug
* Fixed max one "RE:" in reply of messages in forum.
* Fixed so that the forum code runs under the latest version of PHP
* Fixed bug in image view, referer page was not properly set
* Fixed so that users can change their password
* Fixed so that admin can read forum messages.
* Fixed some minor forum bugs.

Changes from version 1.0.2
--------------------------
* Added discussion on articles / news
* Added session timeout on user groups
* Added session info, currently loggen in users
* Added possibility to manually logout users
* Fixed wishlist
* Removed debug output from product view template.
* Lots of bug fixes
* Template cleanup

Changes from version 1.0.1
--------------------------
* Added multiple assignments of products.
* Added hot deals on products.
* Added clickable thumbnail images on product view.
* Added assignment of articles to multiple categories.
* Added showing of customers email address in Order edit.
* Added showing of number of users registered
* Added searchable products.
* Added searchable articles.
* Added welcome message.
* Removed Javascript from the cart.
* Removed broken image on product preview if no image exists.
* Fixed some issues with cache coherence
* Fixed preview of product options.
* Fixed external link on products.
* Fixed deleting of cached printed version, when an article is updated.
* Fixed internationalization of Order list and Order edit.
* Various language updates.

Changes from version 1.0
------------------------
* Added printable version of the articles
* Fixed an calculation error in the mails sendt on order confirmation.
* Fixed editing of user addresses and checking if the user has an address
  before sending an order.